<div class="columns large-12">
  <h2> Using the Guide. </h2>

  <p>
    The styles in this guide are the styles available to the OpenFarm pages by default. They should be used as guidelines and defaults. This page has no additional styles defined (meaning: you can do all of this without building any of your own styles)
  </p>
  <p>
    They're based on Foundation's styles, so anyone familiar with those styles should be familiar with these.
  </p>
  <p>
    If something's not mentioned here, we haven't talked or thought about it yet. We're open to input.
  </p>
</div>
